ZH: 他在学习的时候总是保持虚心。
EN: He always keeps an open mind while learning.

ZH: 她虚心地向老师请教问题。
EN: She humbly asks the teacher for advice.

ZH: 我们应该虚心接受他人的批评。
EN: We should humbly accept criticism from others.

ZH: 他的虚心让他很受欢迎。
EN: His open-mindedness makes him very popular.

